{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "novel-backend-api-collection",
		"name": "Novel Backend API",
		"description": "Complete API collection for Novel Backend application with Role-Based Access Control (RBAC).\n\n## Roles:\n- **ADMIN**: Full access to all features including user/role management\n- **MODERATOR**: Can manage content (stories, chapters, genres) and moderate comments\n- **USER**: Can read content, create comments/ratings, manage own data\n- **PUBLIC**: Read-only access to stories, chapters, genres\n\n## Authentication:\n1. Register or login to get JWT token\n2. Token is automatically saved to collection variables\n3. All authenticated requests use the bearer token\n\n## Admin Endpoints:\n- Require ADMIN role\n- User management: activate/deactivate, assign/remove roles\n- Role management: create, update, delete custom roles\n- Statistics and monitoring\n\n## Testing:\n1. Create users with different roles (USER, MODERATOR, ADMIN)\n2. Login with each role to test different access levels\n3. Admin endpoints are in separate folders",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{jwt_token}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:8080",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "jwt_token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
